.IP \(bu 2
ignoring generated artifacts after dependency or security tasks
.IP \(bu 2
editing published image base references without an explicit discovery
report
.IP \(bu 2
changing pins without a deliberate write step
.IP \(bu 2
treating the latest upstream-supported vendor binary as repository-owned
